title: [Vornavis, Outlands Road]
description: The rounded shapes of low-growing trees stand among the tall grass to the west, but only the rough-bladed grasses common to the unforested outlands cover the ground to the north, south and east.  The jagged silhouette of a ruined wall is just visible atop a rise to the east.
